  10,53,"They ask you ňĻO Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúIs this true?‚ÄĚ Say, ‚ÄúYes, by my Lord! Most certainly it is true! And you will have no escape.‚ÄĚ"
  10,54,"If every wrongdoer were to possess everything in the world, they would surely ransom themselves with it. They will hide ňĻtheirňļ remorse when they see the torment. And they will be judged in all fairness, and none will be wronged"
