  10,57,"O humanity! Indeed, there has come to you a warning from your Lord, a cure for what is in the hearts, a guide, and a mercy for the believers"
  10,58,"Say, ňĻO Prophet,ňļ ‚ÄúIn Allah‚Äôs grace and mercy let them rejoice. That is far better than whatever ňĻwealthňļ they amass.‚ÄĚ"
  10,59,"Ask ňĻthe pagans, O Prophetňļ, ‚ÄúHave you seen that which Allah has sent down for you as a provision, of which you have made some lawful and some unlawful?‚ÄĚ¬†Say, ‚ÄúHas Allah given you authorization, or are you fabricating lies against Allah?‚ÄĚ"
  10,60,"What do those who fabricate lies against Allah expect on Judgment Day? Surely Allah is ever Bountiful to humanity,¬†but most of them are ungrateful"
  10,61,"There is no activity you may be engaged in ňĻO Prophetňļ or portion of the Quran you may be reciting, nor any deed you ňĻallňļ may be doing except that We are a Witness over you while doing it. Not ňĻevenňļ an atom‚Äôs weight is hidden from your Lord on earth or in heaven; nor anything smaller or larger than that, but is ňĻwrittenňļ in a perfect Record"
  10,62,"There will certainly be no fear for the close servants of Allah, nor will they grieve"
  10,63,ňĻThey areňļ those who are faithful and are mindful ňĻof Himňļ
  10,64,For them is good news in this worldly life and the Hereafter. There is no change in the promise of Allah. That is ňĻtrulyňļ the ultimate triumph
  10,65,"Do not let their words grieve you ňĻO Prophetňļ. Surely all honour and power belongs to Allah. He is the All-Hearing, All-Knowing"
  10,66,Certainly to Allah ňĻaloneňļ belong all those in the heavens and all those on the earth. And what do those who associate others with Allah really follow? They follow nothing but assumptions and do nothing but lie
  10,67,He is the One Who has made the night for you to rest in and the day bright. Surely in this are signs for people who listen
  10,68,"They¬†say, ‚ÄúAllah has offspring.‚ÄĚ¬†Glory be to Him! He is the Self-Sufficient. To Him belongs whatever is in the heavens and whatever is on the earth. You have no proof of this! Do you say about Allah what you do not know"
